      <p class="methodology-note">
        GBrain results from PrecisionMemBench evaluation. Full methodology: <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.11325">arXiv:2605.11325</a>. Dataset: <a href="https://huggingface.co/datasets/tenurehq/precisionmembench">HuggingFace</a>. GBrain source: <a href="https://github.com/garrytan/gbrain">github.com/garrytan/gbrain</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="compare-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Need precise memory, not a knowledge base?</h2>
      <p>One container. Sub-15ms. Precision 1.0. No agent platform required. Thirty seconds to install.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/#cta" class="btn-primary">Install Tenure</a>
        <a href="/docs" class="btn-primary" style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);">Read the docs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>